<plot>Exploring the relationship between culture and technology, this film questions our dependency and 'other' life revolving around the symbiotic relationship. The idea is portrayed through a young woman who feels that her life is not as fulfilling as the virtual existence she leads in physical isolation. Making the ultimate transition from the real world into the 'techno world', she seeks the help of an engineer to realize her virtual life in the physical world.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?052387</url></doc>
